hopobject.body: I'm in my first year at university discount prozac no prescription Perhaps weary of repeating the economic and political fallout from the land reform program, Mugabe backtracked a bit this week as he sought to clarify and limit his indigenisation policy in an attempt allay investors' growing concerns. "Where an investor brings in his or her capital, technology, expertise and raw materials, we will not insist on the principle," Mugabe said. "However, where finite natural resources such as minerals were concerned, the country could not be bystanders in their exploitation."
